    	</p>


<p class="leadquote">
            Week 5
        </p>

        <p>
    		Last week, I was trying to collect as much information as 
                possible to make an informed decision regarding which cloud 
                services to use. I have come to the conclusion that we should 
                go ahead with Amazon Web Services. This is because it has 
                suitable coverage, the plans are pocket friendly, the AWS 
